# Donate_Bangladesh 🌱

A responsive web application that allows users to donate to various causes in Bangladesh, such as flood relief and social justice movements. The website keeps track of donations, displays live balance updates, and shows dynamic donation history.

## 🖥️ Live Demo

Coming Soon / [Deploy on Vercel or GitHub Pages]

---

## 🚀 Features

- 💰 Live balance tracking
- 📜 Donation history logging
- 🧮 Real-time donation calculations
- 📱 Fully responsive (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- 🎨 Clean UI using [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/)
- 💾 JavaScript-based donation logic

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5
- Tailwind CSS
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)
- [DaisyUI](https://daisyui.com/) (for UI components)

---

## 📂 Project Structure

donate-bangladesh/
├── assets/ # Images (logo, coin, banners)
├── js/
│ ├── index.js # Main donation logic
│ └── history.js # History rendering logic
├── index.html # Main page
├── README.md # Project info
└── style.css (optional if using Tailwind CLI or CDN)